('unilag','Use of English','Oral English and Phonology',NULL,'What is the term for the study of the sound system of language?','Phonetics','Phonology','Morphology','Syntax','B','Phonology is the branch of linguistics that examines the sound system of language, including the distribution and patterning of speech sounds.','medium',true,false,NOW()),
